{
  "text": "We have the following fundamental estimates for the evolution family U. Its proof was given in [CITATION_1] though for the sake of clarity, we reproduce it here. Proposition 2.2. For x \u2208 X, 0 \u2264 \u03b1 \u2264 1 and t > s, the following hold:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "120075016"
